      "startTime": 186.3994704558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなことないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.3994704558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "雫は絶対アイドルに向いてる。私が保証する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're definitely idol material. I guarantee it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.3661249155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "雫を傷つけようとする人の言葉なんて聞かなくていいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to listen to people who try to hurt you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.7994633351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.7327976857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それよりも、あなたのことが好きで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead‚ listen to the words of those who love you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.7327976857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大切に思ってくれてる人の言葉に耳を傾けて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and care about you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.2661157602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "私のことを……大切に思ってくれてる人……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "People… who care about me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.099459266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.4376675599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうだよ！　私や、おじさんやおばさん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Me‚ your uncle‚ your aunt…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.4376675599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それに、雫が応援してきた沢山のアイドル達……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And all the idols you've been supporting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.4376563702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ファンがアイドルを応援するように、アイドルも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like fans support idols‚ idols",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.7710090313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ステージからファンにエールを送ってるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "send their cheers to fans from the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.3043352438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.3043423646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "それ、分かる気がする……\nアイドルのステージを見ると、元気がわいてくる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I understand…\nWhen I see an idol's performance‚ it gives me energy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.5665186561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "辛いことがあった時は私達を思い出して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When things are tough‚ remember us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.6413847916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルは……私達はいつだって、あなたの味方だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols… we're always on your side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.7413827571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.4913349462
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.4913349462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと大好きなアイドル達のおかげで……\n私は立ち直ることが出来た……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to my sister and my favorite idols…\nI was able to recover…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.7331853227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 254.7357334447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "その後、お父さんの転勤で星見市に引っ越して……\n私は、誰も私のことを知らない高校に通い始めた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ we moved to Hoshimi City because of my dad's transfer…\nAnd I started going to a high school where no one knew me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.6331853227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 264.9709482503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk021.m4a",
      "text": "そして……星見市には、あの『星降る奇跡』\n長瀬麻奈さんを輩出した芸能プロがあるって知った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… I found out that Hoshimi City is home to the talent agency that produced \"The Miracle of the Falling Stars\"‚\nMana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.1998519894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk022.m4a",
      "text": "私は「これだ」って思った……\n私がこの街に来たのは運命なんだって思った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought‚ \"This is it!\"…\nI thought it was fate that I came to this city…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 277.5331853227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 281.9238951039
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "それでアイドルになるために\n星見プロの新人オーディションを受けようと思ったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you decided to take Hoshimi Pro's new idol audition\nto become an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.3333287556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 287.9572447133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk023.m4a",
      "text": "……思ってない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.9572447133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 289.6369373154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも雫ちゃんは\n星見プロのオーディションを受けたんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But Shizuku-chan‚\nyou took Hoshimi Pro's audition‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.6333185831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 295.3650029015
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk024.m4a",
      "text": "最初は、受けるつもりはなかった……\n自分はアイドルに向いてないと思ってたから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I didn't intend to take it…\nI thought I wasn't suited to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.3612549778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 302.7012838196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk025.m4a",
      "text": "陰気で、口下手で、笑うことも出来ない私じゃ……\nファンを元気にすることは出来ないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gloomy‚ awkward‚ unable to smile…\nI couldn't possibly cheer up fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.7333185831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk026.m4a",
      "text": "私はアイドルを応援出来れば十分だった……\nオーディションなんて受ける気はなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was enough for me to just support idols…\nI had no intention of taking the audition…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.8333185831,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}